{
  "texts": [
    "Section 3 details the carefullydesigned pipeline to ensure the feasibility and validity of the task.",
    "A Haystack typically contains 100 documents on a topic, totaling approximately 100k tokens.",
    "We generate a total of 10 Haystacks, each coupled with roughly 10 queries, for a total of 92 SummHay tasks.",
    "Our pipeline can be scaled and applied to other domains.Our second contribution develops SummHay's evaluation protocol, centering on evaluating system outputs on their Coverage of reference insights, and the quality of their Citation.",
    "A manual annotation confirms strong reproducibility of the pro-tocol among knowledgeable annotators (0.77 correlation)."
  ]
}